Caption: Chief guest Mr. M. C. Chagla meeting some of the eminent dignitaries and guests at the convocation
Description: From left: Dr. A. L. Mudaliar, Dr. Rajah Sir Muthiah Chettiar, Mr. C. V. Sethunathan, Mr. Rajagopalan. Mrs. Shanti Sengupto is at the extreme right and Commodore Rabindra Nath Batra is seen in a white uniform (third from right).
